Hi Kailey,

As discussed earlier, from my understanding your vehicle is currently burning oil. The new car warranty for your vehicle is 5 years from 10/24/2016 or 100,000kms whichever occurs first.

Currently the recalls that are applicable to your vehicle are:
1^TRUNK LATCH PARTIAL REPLACE
1^LFA/YFA/AN/TMA/LM/TL/JSN ECM UPDATE & P1326 WIRING AND ENGINE REPLACEMENT

Unfortunately, neither of the outstanding recalls are relative to excessive oil burning. The 10year or 200,000kms extended warranty is only applicable to rod bearing connection not oil consumption. I do see you have taken an extended warranty for your vehicle so we would have to book you in for a diagnostic which would be $132/hr we would then confirm why the vehicle is burning oil and quote what the necessary repairs would be.
